{"tid":1775338,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"黑警要坐一世監！","createTime":"2019-12-08T20:36:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-09T17:06:10.000Z","uid":279279,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7e63b4c369720a4b68bec9892568a943d9a7654f","tid":1775338,"uid":279279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T20:36:15.000Z","msg":"要判啲黑警終身監禁！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1772597\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1772597</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實已經聽過好多次，有被捕手足受到黑警性暴力對待。<br />\n今日法改會重新定義「強姦」，所有入侵性嘅性暴力，都要判<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">終身監禁</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n咁即係唔係淨係強姦女手足嘅黑警要終身監禁，受到其他入侵性性暴力，例如男手足俾爆後門，個黑警一樣要終身監禁。<br />\n<br />\n點樣可以利用今次法改會嘅重新定義，為啲手足<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">討回公道</span></span>？黑警唔止要死全家，仲一定要坐一世監！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/為何建議不再用-強姦-字眼\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E7%82%BA%E4%BD%95%E5%BB%BA%E8%AD%B0%E4%B8%8D%E5%86%8D%E7%94%A8-%E5%BC%B7%E5%A7%A6-%E5%AD%97%E7%9C%BC&d=2Jo0d4zpMW7MEYOmRW2LdUwAUq3ZsepC89uAf1Ef2WI%3D&h=109428a4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E7%82%BA%E4%BD%95%E5%BB%BA%E8%AD%B0%E4%B8%8D%E5%86%8D%E7%94%A8-%E5%BC%B7%E5%A7%A6-%E5%AD%97%E7%9C%BC&h=2595386c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/society/為何建議不再用-強姦-字眼</a>"},{"pid":"3b2563ab09cfd20b366d67031c5049eab4721150","tid":1775338,"uid":167499,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T20:38:44.000Z","msg":"聽過一個講法 如果強姦下下都判最重 咁就會多好多姦殺"},{"pid":"84c3bdeeb1b8602c85d71edbdb21d72da7b7d2f6","tid":1775338,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T20:42:04.000Z","msg":"係黑警就直接死刑啦<br />\n養住都嘥米飯"},{"pid":"9683ec6118ead4e56d66b25458dde4e6cf49c947","tid":1775338,"uid":279279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"q